  "texts": [
    "In this work, we make the following contributions.",
    "• Outcome-driven conversational AI.",
    "We formally define the problem of outcome-driven conversational AI that motivates this work, where an agent receives a sparse reward at the end of the conversation if an outcome is achieved.",
    "We do so through the lens of a motivating application, the Suggested Response problem, a variation on the widely studied chatbot problem, in which the AI agent provides response suggestions to the business rather than generating automatic replies.",
    "• Reduction from multi-turn to single-turn RLHF."
  ],
